I would give my Mom's intended small bequest to a Christian economic development service in Miss. despite my Dad's cash-poverty.  We might not have to ask friends & family to help with Dad's final expenses.  I might be able to fund several years of service in the aforementioned economic development agency, in advance, giving it ?interest income? and such, while I work there?
